                    "company": "The Technical University of Delft",
                    "description": "Researcher in the Cato project about time-lapse seismic monitoring of the permanent storage and migration of CO2 in the subsurface and enhanced production of methane gas. I worked together with Prof. dr. ir. Kees Wapenaar, Dr. Karl-Heinz Wolf and Dr. Danijela Sijacic.",
